im never on here. i dont know why. oh yes i do, im not a livejournal type of person. however, i felt like posting some quotes i found that express how i feel.
I want to scream real loud Will you hear me? I want to cry my eyes out. Will you see me? Do you love me? You said you did. Did you lie? I can't be played like this I'm not your toy But my heart is breaking "then reality kicked in, never been happier than then, those days that still made me smile, when i had perfection for a while." someone mentioned your name and asked if i knew you i just smile ,, look down ,, think of all our good times x3 and then i softly whisper with a tear --"Yeah, i used to" So you found out today your life's not the same Not quite as perfect as it was yesterday but When you were just getting in the groove Now you're faced with something new And I know it hurts and I know you feel torn But you never gave up this easily before So why do you choose today to give it all away when you're a kid, you see the life that you want,and it never crosses your mind that its not gonna turn out that way Dear You, I wanted to let you know that for all the times you made me smile, I thank you. You made me feel whole and like someone really saw who I was inside. This is for you, poor child - who's heart has yet to be loved by another. For your chance at this one has slowly passed. This is for you, Mr.Amazing - for your true colors couldn't have shown so boldly. This is for the tears you made me cry that you never saw. For you can see them now, for there is a mark on my heart. This is for you, oblivious lover - who drifted off unto someplace else. This is for you, an old crush, I have said my goodbyes - & have put you to rest. Love Always,- Me

ive decided i officially hate this school. i hate simi, and i hate everything about this place. i want to just leave. i dont like how they do things. they make my life hell. i hate the system. when i ever i really want something, can i have it? no. this district is hell. thye just want my life to be hell. they want me to die. they want my life to be horrible.

first i want to graduate when i can. but would they let me even if i filled all the requirements? no. why? because the district doesnt want me too. the district here feels that even if a student is more than capable, they still cannot do what they are able to. i could have taken the stupid PE, health and econ/gov classes this year. and then id be eligible to graduate. then i wouldn't have to put up with this stupid school another year. 

next. since the whole world knows how much i LOVE web design. i want to take the new ROP web design class. but since AP english 12 is second period, im already unable to take ROP for that one period. and since i cant take it that one period, im not able to take it during third period even though thats the only period id be able to take it. it makes my life horrible. so then im still stuck in french 3. a class that i took last year. and the only reason why i took it again was to learn imparfait, something i didnt learn last year. so now that ive learned that, im just going to sit in french 3 doing work i did last year, listening to things i heard last year. everything already done. and ill be absolutely bored. i think ill just never show up to that class. just not participate. not do the work. nothing. and then thats a failure on my grade. do i care? no, because this school is putting me to that point. i could do the work, but what is the point. its pointless. absolutely pointless. because its stupid.

i hate it here. i could just call up my mom and tell her that id love to leave. i could move to the philippines, and id get my diploma in about a couple months. then i could just go to college. or not go to college and just be a bum and live there. because one dollar equals 55 pesos, so id be living the high-life, and doing nothing. so why is it that i still want to be in simi? what was my reason for staying again?

life sucks. im bored. i like making webpages. skottie makes me happy. friends are wonderful people. i want to go to a zoo. or magic mountain. eating is nice.

i hate my mom. i can't stand her. she doesn't like me at all. she just hates me. she thinks i cant do anything right. she thinks that im a hopeless failure. she's mad at me because im always talking to scott. its not my fault that we like eachother. okay, you cant stop two people from liking eachother. its the whole romeo&juliette thing. you try to make them stop, and guess what happens. they commit suicide. im not saying that i would do that over anyone, im just saying that it makes a person want to rebel more. 
then she's so naive. she wants me to just focus on school. not to work, have friends, no boyfriend, nothing but school. i mean, who the hell actually only focuses on school. there is no way in hell any person could only be about school. cause honestly everyone has something else going for them. and like, she wants me to go to college. nothing then. she gets pissed off if i have any extra-curriculars or i volunteer, but that is what i need to get into a good college you know? so how the hell does she expect me to get into a four year university when she wont even let me meet all the requirements. she just wants the grades, she doesn't understand that colleges are looking for more than just grades. and even if i get into a college. i cant do anything then. she doesnt want me to work, because she wants me to focus on my classes. she doesn't want me to have any friends, cause that will take time out of studying. she definately wont let me have a boyfriend, because that would just screw me over. so what the hell? when am i going to be allowed to grow up? after college? i dont think so either. she wants me to get into a career, get high up on that ladder. become a president of some company. and in order to do that, am i allowed to have a life? no, i cant, she wants me to spend all my time and energy into that career that she will finally let me have once i graduate from college. any friends? no. any boys? no. she says she wants me to get married one day, but when will that day come? when im dead? dead from not having a life? gosh.

thanks mom. for all the stupid bullshit you have put me through, and are going to. 

i just wish i could grow up now. maybe leave. go away from all the stupid troubles that i have. gah!
</lj-cut>

NICE GUYS FINISH LAST..(to all gurls out there) 

it's amazing that assholes can get girls.actually, now that i think of it it's not that AMAZING.they are assholes at heart, but to meet girls they unlavish their undying love.IT"S A CHARADE.they act nice,friendly, and they listen...until they get into what their after.Their prey thinks that they are in love with them,however when they realize what assholes their predators really are, they pretend like the asshole is really nice inside.the girl tries to change the asshole into a NICE GUY,but assholes will always be assholes.she gets upset and goes to the NICE GUY to complain about the ASSHOLE.but she claims to love the asshole...now this is where the THEORY begins.she does not want to look like she is easy so she won't dump the asshole right away,instead she will stay with the asshole.
